==== ENTRY 1 ====
HEADWORD: Jinny road
<hw>Jin"ny road`</hw> <pr>(?)</pr>. <ety>[Cf. <er>Gin</er> an engine,
<er>Ginnycarriage</er>.]</ety> <fld>(Mining)</fld> <def>An inclined road
in a coal mine, on which loaded cars descend by gravity, drawing up
empty ones.</def> <rj><au>Knight.</au></rj>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><ent>Jinrikisha</ent>⟦br⟧
